# Reef Decor

_**Reef Decor** aims to add decorational blocks, which you can craft out of coral blocks and prismarine blocks, as well as some extras. Currently, **Reef Decor** adds Coral Bricks, Coral Pillars, Polished Coral Blocks, Coral-Infused Prismarine, Smooth Prismarine, and a new block called Purple Shell._

**All blocks have simple recipes:**
- For **Coral Bricks**, simply put 4 Coral Blocks in a Crafting Table in a 2x2 pattern;
- For **Coral Pillars**, simply put 2 Coral Bricks in a Crafting Table in a 2x1 pattern;
- For P**olished Coral Blocks**, simply put 4 Coral Pillars in a Crafting Table in a 2x2 pattern;
- To craft a **Purple Shell**, you'll have to search through Suspicious Sand and Ruined Structures in Warm Oceans, as well as look into Shipwrecks - Once you get 9 Shell Fragments, put them together in a Crafting Table to get the Shell;

We might have some future content for **Reef Decor** planned, so stay tuned!! ^_^ 




_Code written by SaddestShark_

_All art created by WLTCHDAGGER_
